Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Manfrey_Martell\" title=\"Manfrey Martell\">Manfrey Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Obella_Sand\" title=\"Obella Sand\">Obella Sand</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arys_Oakheart\" title=\"Arys Oakheart\">Arys Oakheart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maelys_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Maelys I Blackfyre\">Maelys I Blackfyre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Dayne\" title=\"Gerold Dayne\">Gerold Dayne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Waters\" title=\"Lord of the Waters\">Lord of the Waters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aegon_IV)\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen (daughter of Aegon IV)\">Daenerys Targaryen, daughter of Aegon IV</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_Terms_Mentioned\">Places and Terms Mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and Terms Mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:33;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne<